# LICENSE - OBJ to Tetrahedron Mesh Toolchain

This toolchain consists of three parts: **self-developed code**, a **mesh repair tool based on VCGLib**, and a **third-party tetrahedral meshing component**. Each part is governed by its own license as detailed below.

---

## 1. Self-Developed Code (MIT License)

The following programs and their source code are original work and are licensed under the **MIT License**:
- `obj2ply.py` / `obj2ply.exe` (OBJ to PLY converter)
- `nodele2tet.cpp` / `nodele2tet.exe` (NODE/ELE to TET converter)
- `obj2tet.cpp` / `obj2tet.exe` (One‑click OBJ → TET workflow tool)

